perfcenter.baseclass

Class Scenario

  • java.lang.Object
    • perfcenter.baseclass.Scenario
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ScenarioSim

    public class Scenario
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds a Scenario, as defined in the input file. It also holds some basic performance metrics of the scenario, which can be filled in after the system is solved.
    Author:
    akhila
